00:29:57.325 --> 00:29:58.700 align:middle line:84%
In quantum mechanics,
when you do

00:29:58.700 --> 00:30:00.980 align:middle line:90%
the angular momentum, the way--

00:30:00.980 --> 00:30:02.030 align:middle line:90%
it's the same thing.

00:30:02.030 --> 00:30:08.660 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, here, we just generalize
