00:30:08.660 --> 00:30:10.130 align:middle line:90%
Yes?

00:30:10.130 --> 00:30:14.070 align:middle line:84%
AUDIENCE: So it was some similar
question, but just like--

00:30:14.070 --> 00:30:15.640 align:middle line:84%
