00:30:41.220 --> 00:30:43.350 align:middle line:84%
Essentially, that's
how you-- yeah,

00:30:43.350 --> 00:30:45.570 align:middle line:84%
this is how you
build the algebra,

00:30:45.570 --> 00:30:47.520 align:middle line:90%
because the algebra is also--

00:30:47.520 --> 00:30:50.490 align:middle line:84%
the finite
transformation is also

00:30:50.490 --> 00:30:53.520 align:middle line:84%
built up by infinitesimal
transformations.

00:30:53.520 --> 00:30:55.950 align:middle line:90%
And so essentially guaranteed--

00:30:55.950 --> 00:30:59.280 align:middle line:84%
yeah, so there is
a theory of groups

00:30:59.280 --> 00:31:01.340 align:middle line:90%
and the algebra behind this.

00:31:01.340 --> 00:31:03.920 align:middle line:90%
Yes, I didn't go into that.

00:31:03.920 --> 00:31:05.810 align:middle line:84%
So some of you may
