00:31:34.640 --> 00:31:38.910 align:middle line:84%
So if you consider all
the spatial components,

00:31:38.910 --> 00:31:41.810 align:middle line:84%
and if you consider
all the edge here,

00:31:41.810 --> 00:31:43.980 align:middle line:84%
then these are the
angular momentum operator,

00:31:43.980 --> 00:31:46.130 align:middle line:84%
and this is your
standard angular momentum

00:31:46.130 --> 00:31:47.510 align:middle line:90%
operator, which you have seen.

00:31:47.510 --> 00:31:50.540 align:middle line:84%
And if you look at 0
i, and then that's what

00:31:50.540 --> 00:31:52.430 align:middle line:90%
