00:31:52.430 --> 00:31:54.350 align:middle line:90%
It generates the boost.

00:31:54.350 --> 00:31:59.300 align:middle line:84%
But in terms of the
conserved number,

00:31:59.300 --> 00:32:04.377 align:middle line:84%
we don't use it in the essential
way-- say, in other contexts.

00:32:04.377 --> 00:32:05.210 align:middle line:90%
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:32:05.210 --> 00:32:05.870 align:middle line:90%
PROFESSOR: Yes?

00:32:05.870 --> 00:32:07.328 align:middle line:84%
AUDIENCE: But to
that question, you

00:32:07.328 --> 00:32:09.500 align:middle line:84%
