00:41:23.640 --> 00:41:25.220 align:middle line:84%
This is just the
canonical momentum

00:41:25.220 --> 00:41:29.490 align:middle line:90%
for the canonical quantization.

00:41:29.490 --> 00:41:31.680 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, this is not the
