00:41:31.680 --> 00:41:34.080 align:middle line:84%
AUDIENCE: Then is the
adjoint of the field operator

00:41:34.080 --> 00:41:36.450 align:middle line:90%
the same thing as the star?

00:41:36.450 --> 00:41:39.150 align:middle line:84%
PROFESSOR: Yeah, here, we
